snippet.title: Super FNaF Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
The first trailer for my current project "Super Five Nights at Freddy's" is finally public!

The game is basically a platformer and adventure game, which focuses on the spirit children trying to avenge their deaths at the hand of the purple guy. It takes place in the FNaF 1 pizzeria with over 20 rooms to explore, as well as other scenery, like Fredbears, Fazbears Fright and other environments.

http://gamejolt.com/games/super-fnaf/158082
